00:17:59.076 --> 00:18:04.969
Mataji Nirmala Devi priityartam -
Sarva devi deva…

00:18:05.170 --> 00:18:07.778
Pujari e gli yogi: … Sakshat
Shri Adi Shakti Bhagavati Mataji

00:18:07.979 --> 00:18:11.508
Shri Nirmala Devyai
Namoh Namah.

